Build a library

Print Labels on Invitation Card
    Given a list of records
        Input Format:-
            firstName,lastName,gender,age,city,state,country
    Output format:-
        a.Mr/Ms First Last
        b.Mr/Ms Last First
        Prefix -
            Male - Mr
            Female - Ms
        c.Mr/Ms First Last country
        d.Mr/Ms Last First country

-----------------------------------------------------------

$ cat records.txt
    firstName,lastName,gender,age,city,state,country

Usages:-
    $ ./LabelPrinter -f records.txt

    $ ./LabelPrinter --firstLast records.txt

    $ ./LabelPrinter -l records.txt

    $ ./LabelPrinter --lastFirst records.txt

    $ ./LabelPrinter -fc records.txt

    $ ./LabelPrinter --firstLastCountry records.txt

    $ ./LabelPrinter -lc records.txt

    $ ./LabelPrinter --lastFirstCountry records.txt

